@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((0.55 / wp.cos(v0 + 0.96)) / (v2 - wp.exp(tmp + 0.52)))
    v0 = (wp.sin(wp.cos(v0 + 0.58)) + wp.exp((v0 + 0.56 / tmp + 0.65)))
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.abs((v0 + 0.67 + v1 + 0.49)))
    v2 = (0.71 * 0.34)
    tmp = ((0.94 - (v2 + 0.38 / tmp + 0.70)) + (wp.cos(tmp + 0.39) + (v0 + 0.81 - v2 + 0.35)))
    tmp = (((v2 + 0.88 - v0 + 0.35) / tmp) * tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
